<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Pendaftaran Jadwal Konsultasi</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-10 mb-10 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
    <div class="bg-cyan-400 text-white text-center py-5 text-xl font-bold">
      Pembayaran Konsultasi
    </div>
    <div class="p-6">
      <form method="post" action="/views/jadwalkan-konsultasi-3antrian.ejs" class="space-y-6">

      <section>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Nominal Transfer</h4>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-500">Rp <%= data.nominal %></p> 
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">QRIS</h2>
        <img src="/images/qris.png" alt="dump-qris" class="w-32 h-32 mb-4">
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Transfer Bank</h2>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <p><strong>Bank Penerima:</strong> BCA</p>
          <p><strong>Nomor Rekening:</strong> 1234567890</p>
          <p class="text-blue-500">Proses verifikasi kurang dari 10 menit setelah pembayaran berhasil.</p>
          <p>Menerima tranfer dari semua Bank termasuk <strong>Bank Syariah</strong>.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <!-- Accordion 1 -->
        <details class="border-b">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <span class="font-medium">Petunjuk Mobile Banking</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-4 text-sm">
            <p>1. Login ke aplikasi Mobile Banking bank kamu.</p>
            <p>2. Pilih menu Transfer.</p>
            <p>3. Pilih Transfer ke Bank Lain atau Transfer Antar Rekening, sesuai tujuan.</p>
            <p>4. Masukkan nomor rekening tujuan.</p>
            <p>5. Masukkan jumlah transfer sesuai yang diinginkan.</p>
            <p>6. Periksa kembali detail transfer.</p>
            <p>7. Masukkan PIN atau verifikasi dengan OTP (jika diminta).</p>
            <p>8. Simpan atau screenshot bukti transfer.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Accordion 2 -->
        <details class="border-b">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <span class="font-medium">Petunjuk Transfer Bank</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="pb-4 text-sm">
            <p>1. Masukkan kartu ATM dan PIN.</p>
            <p>2. Pilih menu Transfer.</p>
            <p>3. Pilih Transfer ke Bank Lain.</p>
            <p>4. Masukkan nomor rekening tujuan.</p>
            <p>5. Masukkan jumlah transfer sesuai dengan nominal.</p>
            <p>6. Periksa kembali detail transfer.</p>
            <p>7. Konfirmasi transfer dan simpan bukti transaksi.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

      </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Buttons -->
      <div class="flex justify-end gap-3 pr-6 pb-4">
        <button class="px-5 py-2 bg-cyan-400 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-cyan-500">Lanjut</button>
      </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
